{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162710/extras/description0_1.gif?t=1727905291\" /><br>Leonardo's Island DEMO is an adventure/building game set in the age of pirates, featuring wooden constructions and sailboats. <br><br><strong>This is a demo version of the game. Some story missions are reserved for the full release. <br>Surfing and ship construction are not included in this demo. <br>However, all terrain construction items will unlock once you complete all demo missions.</strong><br><br>You left the comfort of your parents' house in search of adventure, treasure, and freedom. But now, you find yourself alone on the island as pirates approach. It\u2019s time to take action!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162710/extras/building.png?t=1727905291\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162710/extras/resources1.gif?t=1727905291\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162710/extras/building1.gif?t=1727905291\" /><br><br>Create your new home, design your flag, hang a hammock, and relax! <br>Build structures to complete the campaign, dive for cannons, and protect the island!<br><br>You can build your own ships with 1, 2, or 5 sails \u2014 the design is entirely up to you!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162710/extras/boatbuilding1.gif?t=1727905291\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162710/extras/battles.png?t=1727905291\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162710/extras/battles1.gif?t=1727905291\" /><br><br>Fortification is key in defending against pirates.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" sr